OL,4,Cold's sepsis death - inquest
OL,6,FNeglect by medical professionals
OL,7,Fcontributed to the death of a three-
OL,8,Fyear-old boy from sepsis, an inquest
OL,9,Fhas found.
OL,11,FOscar Neillings died at Chesterfield
OL,12,FRoyal Hospital in November 2023, about
OL,13,Fa week after contracting a
OL,14,Fstreptococcus (strep A) infection.
OL,16,FAn inquest at Chesterfield Coroner's
OL,17,FCourt heard two GPs had misdiagnosed
OL,18,Fhis cold symptoms as a viral infection.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/11
