OL,4,Cold's sepsis death - inquest
OL,6,FHe was transferred to hospital after
OL,7,Fanother visit to a GP but was not
OL,8,Fgiven antibiotics for more than two
OL,9,Fhours after arriving and suffered a
OL,10,Ffatal cardiac arrest the same evening.
OL,12,FThe jury found Oscar died from natural
OL,13,Fcauses contributed to by neglect.
OL,15,FSpeaking after the inquest, Oscar's
OL,16,Fmother, Stephanie, 33, said: "Our
OL,17,Fdarling little boy Oscar was taken
OL,18,Faway from us and he can't come back.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/11
