OL,6,F"We long for how our life used to be,
OL,7,Fbut we have to adapt to this new
OL,8,Fnormal, carry on and carry Oscar with
OL,9,Fus."
OL,11,FThe inquest, at Chesterfield Coroner's
OL,12,FCourt, heard Oscar developed a cold
OL,13,Fabout a week before his death.
OL,15,FAs his symptoms worsened, his parents
OL,16,Ftwice called the NHS 111 helpline,
OL,17,Fleading to separate out-of-hours GP
OL,18,Fappointments.
