OL,4,Cold's sepsis death - inquest
OL,6,FMedical experts told the hearing
OL,7,FOscar's care was fragmented and lacked
OL,8,Furgency, and that national sepsis
OL,9,Fprotocols - including early fluid
OL,10,Fresuscitation, timely antibiotics, and
OL,11,Fcritical care escalation - were not
OL,12,Ffollowed.
OL,14,FAssistant coroner Julie Mitchell had
OL,15,Finstructed the jury to examine whether
OL,16,Fthere were "missed opportunities to
OL,17,Ftreat or escalate his care" and if
OL,18,F"failures had any material bearing" on
OL,19,Fhis death.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/11
