OL,6,FMrs Neillings added: "I knew he wasn't
OL,7,Fwell, but I was dismissed and his care
OL,8,Ffelt completely chaotic and
OL,9,Finconsistent. I wondered, could this
OL,10,Fbe sepsis, but didn't verbalise that.
OL,12,F"I thought I was going mad. For
OL,13,Fmedical professionals not to recognise
OL,14,Fit - it's something I'll never
OL,15,Funderstand.
OL,17,F"Oscar was seen by numerous doctors.
OL,18,FSome acknowledged the possibility of
OL,19,Fsepsis, yet it still wasn't treated.
OL,20,FThat failure is devastating.
