OL,6,FHelen Reynolds, medical negligence
OL,7,Flawyer at Fletchers Solicitors, the
OL,8,Ffirm representing the family in a
OL,9,Fcivil claim against the trust, said:
OL,10,F"This inquest has brought painful
OL,11,Fclarity to what went so tragically
OL,12,Fwrong in Oscar's case. The failings in
OL,13,Fhis care are deeply distressing. But
OL,14,Fthe family's courage in sharing their
OL,15,Fstory must lead to action."
