OL,6,FDr Ron Daniels, founder of the UK
OL,7,FSepsis Trust, said: "Every day at the
OL,8,FUK Sepsis Trust (UKST) we hear stories
OL,9,Fjust like Oscar's: about the terrible
OL,10,Fconsequences of failing to spot and
OL,11,Ftreat the key signs of sepsis swiftly.
OL,12,FSurviving sepsis ` particularly for
OL,13,Fchildren but for people of all ages `
OL,14,Fshould not come down to advocacy or a
OL,15,Fpostcode lottery.
