OL,6,F"We need improved public awareness of
OL,7,Fsepsis, and a commitment from health
OL,8,Fministers on the development and
OL,9,Fimplementation of a uniform and
OL,10,Fresourced 'sepsis pathway' - a
OL,11,Fstandardised treatment plan that
OL,12,Fensures patients receive the right
OL,13,Fcare from the point at which they
OL,14,Fpresent their symptoms to a clinician
OL,15,Fthrough to receiving their diagnosis."
