OL,6,FKrishna Kallianpur, executive chief
OL,7,Fnurse at Chesterfield Royal Hospital
OL,8,FNHS Trust, said: "At the heart of this
OL,9,Fis a family who have lost their three-
OL,10,Fyear-old son and for that we offer our
OL,11,Fsincere condolences.
OL,13,F"We have submitted a full learning
OL,14,Freview and acknowledge the findings of
OL,15,Fthe coroner with the conclusion of
OL,16,Fnatural causes contributed to by
OL,17,Fneglect. We will continue to embed the
OL,18,Factions taken to date to ensure that
OL,19,Fwe continue to learn and improve."
